<attribute name="Sentiment" >-0.200000003</attribute>
<attribute name="Sentiments" >-0.4;0.2;-0.4</attribute>
<attribute name="Width" >5</attribute>
<attribute name="Xpos" >94.5</attribute>
<attribute name="Ypos" >0</attribute>
<text >In this lab, you will deploy a trained model and perform a prediction against the model. You will then delete the endpoint and perform a batch transform on the test dataset.

Note: The model is created for you in the notebook as part of the setup.</text>
