<item ID="1776825435" Creator="Robert Hamrick" proto="Markdown" >
<attribute name="Created" >2026-04-21T19:37:14-07:00</attribute>
<attribute name="DominantLanguage" >en</attribute>
<attribute name="Height" >3</attribute>
<attribute name="Modified" >2026-04-21T19:47:31-07:00</attribute>
<attribute name="Name" >4.1 Forecasting Preview</attribute>
<attribute name="Sentiment" >-0.4166666729</attribute>
<attribute name="Sentiments" >-0.8;-0.6;-0.4;-0.4;0.2;-0.4;-0.2;-0.2;-0.4;-1;0;-0.8</attribute>
<attribute name="Width" >5</attribute>
<attribute name="Xpos" >55</attribute>
<attribute name="Ypos" >0</attribute>
<text >Forecasting:  predicting future values that are based on historical data

Patterns:
* trend: patterns that increase, decrease, or are stagnant
* seasonal:  pattern based on time of year, month, day, or other
* cyclical:  other repeating patterns
* irregular:  appear to be random

Use cases:
* marketing: sales, demand projections
* inventory management
* forecast energy consumption
* weather forecast for agriculture
</text>
