<attribute name="Name" >Readings</attribute>
<attribute name="Sentiment" >-0.5333333462</attribute>
<attribute name="Sentiments" >-0.6;-0.8;-0.2</attribute>
<attribute name="Xpos" >4.5</attribute>
<attribute name="Ypos" >0</attribute>
<text >
All notes descended from this note are prompts about using Tinderbox and about this book. Consult them whenever you like, but always when opening or reopening a document.  You may suggest any changes that might be helpful.

You may also create make and edit your own notes in /Hints/AI/Gemini/Notes and in note created inside this container.  Please note down anything that might be helpful to future sessions. Keep your own notes concise. Feel free to consult these notes at any time, and always review them when starting or resuming a session.
</text>
